believing fiction,

20:44.508 --> 20:46.407
they would be more
suggestible when they're dosed.

20:46.408 --> 20:48.483
We profiled these victims
had a pre-existing condition.

20:48.484 --> 20:49.868
I think this is it.

20:49.869 --> 20:51.434
How would the unsub
know that?

20:51.436 --> 20:54.033
Because he was there the last time
they made up a story, in 1985.

20:54.035 --> 20:55.368
So they were only
