of the satanic ritual abuse allegations.

21:03.146 --> 21:05.249
Oh, crap.

21:05.251 --> 21:07.153
This is a completely
different set of circumstances.

21:07.155 --> 21:09.083
Was it? Throughout the 1980s,
pre-school-age kids

21:09.085 --> 21:10.858
made accusations
against their teachers.

21:10.860 --> 21:13.555
McMartin, Fells Acres,
Kern County.

21:13.557 --> 21:15.062
270 cases by 1988.

21:15.064 --> 21:17.600
Numerous innocent teachers
had their careers and lives ruined,

21:17.602 --> 21:19.906
