the same thing, that they saw this.

21:35.614 --> 21:37.379
3-year-old Larry Merrin
would have said

21:37.381 --> 21:39.252
the monster dragged him
down the stairs.

21:39.254 --> 21:42.125
And 4-year-old Daniel Karras
one-upped it by adding a sexual detail.

21:42.127 --> 21:43.293
That's how kids
tell stories,

21:43.295 --> 21:44.789
especially when
they're reinforced

21:44.791 --> 21:46.491
by well-meaning parents,
therapists, and cops.

21:46.493 --> 21:48.324
And in doing so,
they ruin the unsub's life,

21:48.326 --> 21:49.732
