37:06.020 --> 37:07.826
Morgan!

37:07.828 --> 37:08.826
Uhh!

37:14.301 --> 37:16.899
Now I know
what scares you.

37:16.901 --> 37:17.930
No!

37:17.932 --> 37:20.099
No!

37:23.310 --> 37:25.815
Son of a bitch.

37:25.817 --> 37:28.218
Son of a bitch...

37:34.829 --> 37:36.594
It's ok.

37:36.596 --> 37:39.464
You can move now.

37:50.041 --> 37:51.703
Here.

37:51.705 --> 37:53.871
I have something for you.

37:59.742 --> 38:03.280
I'm about to come
through that front door.

38:03.282 --> 38:04.910
Kill me

38:04.912 --> 38:07.612
before I kill you.

38:09.779 --> 38:11.543
Rossi, Reid, take the front.

38:11.545 --> 38:13.206
JJ and I will take the back.

38:13.208 --> 38:16.475
Watch your front sight.
One of ours is in there.

38:16.477 --> 38:18.611
My gun.

38:18.613 --> 38:21.213
I need my gun.

38:25.391 --> 38:27.725
Look. Here I come.

38:27.727 --> 38:29.629
Kill me.

38:52.781 --> 38:55.083
Hotch!

38:56.084 --> 38:57.821
We need a medic in here!

38:57.823 --> 39:00.959
Rossi, take it.

39:00.961 --> 39:04.401
They made me see things.

39:04.403 --> 39:06.098
They made me see things.

39:06.100 --> 39:07.435
Ok.

39:07.437 --> 39:09.036
He's gone.

39:20.617 --> 39:22.551
We got him.

39:41.309 --> 39:42.539
I win.

39:42.541 --> 39:44.707
I don't think so.

39:44.709 --> 39:49.074
You have no idea
what I did to him.

39:49.076 --> 39:50.649
I win.

39:57.124 --> 39:59.321
He surrendered.

39:59.323 --> 40:00.953
Ambulance is on its way.

40:00.955 --> 40:02.225
He surrendered?
That doesn't make sense.

40:02.227 --> 40:03.321
We need to get you
looked at.

40:03.323 --> 40:04.455
I'm fine.

40:04.457 --> 40:08.388
Hey, this is
not a suggestion.

40:41.269 --> 40:43.801
I'm fine. Thank you.

40:47.605 --> 40:50.106
You have to talk
about it.

40:50.108 --> 40:51.105
Not tonight.

40:51.107 --> 40:52.472
Yes, tonight,

40:52.474 --> 40:53.745
while it's still fresh.

40:53.747 --> 40:55.114
I can't.

40:55.116 --> 40:57.285
It doesn't...

40:57.287 --> 40:59.789
Parts of it don't
make sense to me.

40:59.791 --> 41:01.285
They don't have to.

41:01.287 --> 41:03.325
Tell me
what it smelled like.

41:03.327 --> 41:04.860
Tell me how you felt.

41:04.862 --> 41:09.062
Start at the beginning,
start at the end, I don't care. But start.

41:09.064 --> 41:13.738
Now, what do you remember?

41:16.245 --> 41:18.275
Aaron.

41:20.084 --> 41:22.079
Aaron.

41:25.510 --> 41:27.147
Hotch?

41:29.347 --> 41:32.415
This is what happened.

